This plugin will check the status of a local Adaptec AAC-RAID.
It will provide what type of errors that has ouccured count them and output an error row.
Depending on user settings in -w and -c giving WARNING and CRITICAL message at different points.

Based on script by M.Koettenstorfer
https://www.monitoringexchange.org/inventory/Check-Plugins/Hardware/Devices/RAID-Controller/check_arcconf---Adaptec-AAC-RAID
Made some bugfixes and small changes.

Released under GNU/GPL v3 by request from author.

